  "title": "AU Nurse (Private / Office Hours)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company’s Profile:</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading specialist clinic in breast care equipped with high quality services delivered by a team of dedicated healthcare professionals. They provide comprehensive services including breast screening, diagnosis and surgery. Together with their outstanding team, they are looking for a qualified AU Nurse to join their dynamic environment!</p><p>Work Location: Orchard OR Novena</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare patients and theatre for anaesthetic procedures.</li><li>Assist Anaesthetists with preparation of anaesthetic equipment, medications, IV access and patient monitoring.</li><li>Manage monitoring, airway equipment, medications, and documentation.</li><li>Maintain high standards of infection control, patient safety and equipment management.</li><li>Support safe patient transfer and early recovery in PACU.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Registered Nurse with Singapore Nursing Board</li><li>BCLS & AED Certified</li><li>Degree or Diploma in Nursing</li><li>At least 1 – 2 years’ AU Nurse in clinic setting</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates may <strong>whatsapp your resume to 8977 7062</strong>. Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.<br /><br />By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p>Cassie Chan | R2197426</p><p>EnviroDynamics Solutions Pte Ltd |EA No: 12C6285</p>",
